{"tid":1475111,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"藍絲出有假聯署 大家麻煩去投訴佢煽動恐怖主義","createTime":"2019-08-15T11:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T12:03:04.000Z","uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"554047df50a9621988ae4684d595d31ea708c486","tid":1475111,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:16:44.000Z","msg":"假聯署<br />\n同身邊嘅人講「唔好簽」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發現【假】五大訴求聯署<br />\n好多人冇睇內文中伏<br />\n內文話要政府做出五大訴求，然而五大訴求係要求政府嚴正執法鎮壓運動！<br />\n<br />\n文宣組唔該幫手宣揚呢個聯署係假嘅（內文係支持政府鎮壓）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/香港受夠了-五大訴求-撥亂反正-enough-for-hong-kong-5-demands-to-restore-law-and-order\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%97%E5%A4%A0%E4%BA%86-%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-%E6%92%A5%E4%BA%82%E5%8F%8D%E6%AD%A3-enough-for-hong-kong-5-demands-to-restore-law-and-order&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=cb7f6455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/香港受夠了-五大訴求-撥亂反正-enough-for-hong-kong-5-demands-to-restore-law-and-order</a><br />\n<br />\n對家仲諗住登報紙聲稱好多人支持，已經有幾萬人簽咗！<br />\n另外中共開始用三毛四方八面入侵，話示威者暴力同滿口謊言，文宣一定要大大力咁還擊！否則後果不堪設想！<br />\n<br />\n記住<br />\n唔好簽！<br />\n唔好簽！<br />\n唔好簽！<br />\n<br />\n但係要同人講<br />\n個聯署係假嘅！<br />\n咪中伏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上面原文<br />\n<br />\n拉到下面有得report<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bdoK0GK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbdoK0GK.png&h=82821815&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktGD48q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktGD48q.png&h=27eafb84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1eded94489fcd9f133faec45939111d3376105b","tid":1475111,"uid":296952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:17:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">NOW OR NEVER</span></span></strong><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PKKikG4.jpg\" data